I don&#x27;t know if it&#x27;s proper meditation, but right after waking up I sit on the floor and repeat for 20 minutes:<p><i>“Watch your thoughts, they become words;
watch your words, they become actions;
watch your actions, they become habits;
watch your habits, they become character;
watch your character, for it becomes your destiny.”</i><p>It&#x27;s like a mantra. I&#x27;m not even sure about the original source of this quote. It may sound a crazy thing to do, but it helps me focus throughout the day.
